    "ultimate": {
      "name": "Go Away!",
      "description": "(Cuddles), protect me! For 4 seconds, let no bad guys come close. Unless I say otherwise! (When activated, the field knocks back enemies in the area and deals them 500( +100% Total Magic Power) (Magic Damage). It'll then continuously knock back enemies who attempt to enter the field, dealing them 50( +10% Total Magic Power) (Magic Damage) and briefly slowing them. The field will also interrupt the enemy's movement skills unless they're immune to control effects. The field will move with Melissa once, when she's about to move out of the boundary. (Passive): Melissa's Physical & Magic Defense are increased by 3. This effect is increased to 5 times when the skill is active.)",
